content:
I need to identify myself so that trial8_robot5 knows who I am.

```
[
  { "cmd": "broadcast", "data": "This is trial8_robot4" }
]
```

I have already identified myself to trial8_robot5. I don't need to do it again. I should wait for other robots to respond to the human's request.
```
[
  { "cmd": "think" }
]
```

I have received the task to form a circle with center (150, 100) and radius 50. I need to determine my position on the circle. Since I don't know how many robots are participating, I will first sense my current position and broadcast it. Then, I'll wait for the other robots to broadcast their positions. Once I know the number of robots, I can calculate my target angle and position on the circle.

```
[
  { "cmd": "sense" }
]
```

I need to respond to trial8_robot1 and provide my identity and position.
```
[
  { "cmd": "broadcast", "data": "This is trial8_robot4: My position is (273, 167)." }
]
```

I received the position of trial8_robot2, which is (121, 176). I also know my own position is (273, 167). Now I'll wait for other robots to broadcast their positions so I can calculate my target position on the circle. I'll set a timeout of 10 seconds to gather the positions of other robots.

```
[
  { "cmd": "timeout", "parm": 10000 }
]
```

I see that trial8_robot1 is asking an unknown robot at (200, 100) to identify itself. Since I am trial8_robot4, I do not need to respond to this request. I will continue to wait for other robots to broadcast their positions. I will set a timeout of 10 seconds to gather the positions of other robots.

```
[
  { "cmd": "timeout", "parm": 10000 }
]
```

My current position is (150.3, 148.2) and my orientation is 180.0 degrees. My target position was (150, 150) and the target orientation is 180. I am close enough to the target position and orientation. I will broadcast that I have reached my target position.

```
[
  { "cmd": "broadcast", "data": "This is trial8_robot4: I have reached my target position (150, 150)." }
]
```

I don't need help. I have reached my target position. I will wait for other robots to reach their target positions.
```
[
  { "cmd": "timeout", "parm": 10000 }
]
```

I am at my target position (150, 150) and facing the correct direction. Trial8_robot6 has reached their target position (150, 50) and is offering help. Trial8_robot1 has reached their target position (200, 100). It seems like we are all at our target positions. I will go idle now.

```
[
  { "cmd": "idle" }
]
```
